rows.label: bf06470100_0010
rows.name: So it's a site of a fight against him...

rows.label: bf06470100_0020
rows.name: Say, what are these [System:Ruby rt=Devices ]Servants[/System:Ruby], anyway?

rows.label: bf06470100_0040
rows.name:
We've never even seen Siren, just
that light thing it shoots down.

rows.label: bf06470100_0050
rows.name:
A power given to the Heavenly Grail the sword of God 
sleeping in the distant paradise in the sky.

rows.label: bf06470100_0060
rows.name: M-maybe Eden is actually a pretty terrifying place...

rows.label: bf06470100_0080
rows.name: What do you mean "I don't know"...

rows.label: bf06470100_0090
rows.name:
All that I can find in the corners of my memory
is that townscape...

rows.label: bf06470100_0100
rows.name: Why did [System:Ruby rt=Father ]God[/System:Ruby] create me, or the Devices...

rows.label: bf06470100_0120
rows.name: It's okay. We'll find out once we get there.

rows.label: bf06470100_0140
rows.name:
You don't know what's in a treasure chest 
until you open it.

rows.label: bf06470100_0145
rows.name: But if you don't open it, it's just a box.

rows.label: bf06470100_0150
rows.name: That's Salvager's Code number 4, you know.

rows.label: bf06470100_0170
rows.name: Don't equate it with a Salvager's motto.
